ED_Title: Appointment of the members of the Credentials Committee
ED_DecisionText: At its 1st plenary meeting, on 5 September 2023, the General Assembly, in accordance with rule 28 of its rules of procedure, appointed a Credentials Committee for its seventy-eighth session consisting of the following Member States: ANDORRA, CHINA, GRENADA, NIGERIA, RUSSIAN FEDERATION, SOLOMON ISLANDS, SURINAME, TOGO and UNITED STATES OF AMERICA.
ED_Disclaimer: The final text of this decision will be contained in document A/78/49 (Vol. II) after editorial review.
